<h3 class="heading-size-5">Examples</h3>

<p>You can initiaite multiple carousels on multiple elements if you wish for them to have different options:</p>

<p class="alert-bar-info">In order for your carousel to receive the One-Nexus carousel styles, you must give it a class beginning with <code class="alt">carousel-</code>, e.g. <code class="alt">carousel-products</code>

<pre><code class="html">&lt;div class="carousel-products">
    &lt;img src="http://lorempixel.com/640/480" />
    &lt;img src="http://lorempixel.com/640/480" />
    &lt;img src="http://lorempixel.com/640/480" />
    &lt;img src="http://lorempixel.com/640/480" />
&lt;/div></code></pre>

<pre><code>$('.carousel-products').carousel({
    owl: {
        items: 2,
        margin: 20
    }
});</code></pre>

